title: SEND_DUI_MESSAGE

0xCD380DA9// SendDuiMessage
void SEND_DUI_MESSAGE(long duiObject, char* jsonString);Parameters:duiObject: The DUI browser handle.jsonString: The message, encoded as JSON.Sends a message to the specific DUI root page. This is similar to SEND_NUI_MESSAGE.
